bib.title: Average neutron total cross sections in the 3-to 12-MeVregion

free_txt: BP: Updated to new date formats, lower
case. corrections according last EXFOR rules and
Dict. Added doi, REL-REF, LA report, facility, method,
No corrections have been made on the measured cross
sections for the effect of neutrons scattered into the
detector by the sample. The geometry is such that
this correction is probably less than 1.5 percent at
The data from 6 to 13 MeV were obtained by using the
Los Alamos fast reactor as previously described,
while the 3- to 6-MeV data were acquired by using a
U235 converter placed in a hole which goes through
the center of the Los Alamos water boiler.
